        "authorUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111249982692491129753/reviews",
        "rating": 1,
        "text": "DO NOT LIVE HERE! Elevator is broken every other week, door call button doesn’t work regularly, staff is nice but kicking out residents to renovate a unit is insane. Amenities are mid.\n\nShoutout maintenance guy Sosa",
