        "authorUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104900172904484710566/reviews",
        "rating": 5,
        "text": "I would like to start by Thanking the staff at The Paramount, for their exceptional professionalism kindness and awareness. We lived here for 1 year but at the time of renewal we had to make a tough decision and move back to the Midwest. Miss LaTese was always helpful with answering our questions and assisting with overall requests. The maintenance staff was always prompt and courteous and very mindful. The daily cleaning staff always had the halls, lobby and corridors looking and smelling clean. The Paramount was not our first choice when moving to Arlington, yet we found it on a whim and so glad we did. Overall our stay here was a 10/10 experience. We loved our neighborhood and surely will miss it.",
