        "authorPhotoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwUoDT7aVjIOsZkLjjx7kjgxM4nlg6oOl-KLXkv2hHIzpJQA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
        "authorUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116467378904591171774/reviews",
        "rating": 5,
        "text": "Marieme was extremely helpful throughout my apartment transfer process. She was professional, responsive, and made the transition smooth and stress-free. She took the time to explain the available options, answered all my questions, and ensured everything was handled efficiently. I truly appreciate her excellent customer service and would highly recommend her to anyone looking for assistance at The Potomac at RiverHouse Apartments.",
        "publishTime": "2026-05-29T22:40:41.567736604Z",
        "reviewUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toWVYwOW9jbFJCUkRaelJtOHdZM2t4V2pkdmNGRRAB!2m1!1s0x89b7b6dc1444dd51:0x8c6e7a622c86e11e",
        "source": "google"
