        "authorUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109996284821224524672/reviews",
        "rating": 5,
        "text": "Moved in a few weeks ago and love it so far! The building has everything we were looking for.\n\nA few reasons that make it great:\n- Tee made the move-in process easy, even with us coming from out of state and moving in on a major holiday.\n- Great location close to the Metro and walkable to grocery stores, shops, restaurants, gyms, etc.\n- Within walking distance of Georgetown (or short bus ride) for work.\n- The apartment is roomy, quiet and comfortable and is thoughtfully updated. The view is a bonus.\n- Maintenance has been quick, responsive and thorough.\n- The enclosed loading dock and freight elevator make moving in and out of the building a breeze.\n- The gym has everything I need for a full workout.\n- Bike storage included in rent\n- On-site garage parking at a reasonable rate",
